his email. If the proposed time does not work for you, kindly suggest alternative slots that fit your schedule.\\n\\nWe look forward to speaking with you.\\n\\nBest regards,\\n[Your Name]\\n[Your Title]\\n[Company Name]\\n[Contact Information]\\n\\n\\n-- Follow-Up Email (if no response in 2 days) --\\n\\nSubject: Reminder: Interview Invitation – Software Engineer Position\\n\\nDear [Candidate Name],\\n\\nI hope you’re doing well. I wanted to follow up on the interview invitation we sent on [Date of Original Email] for the Software Engineer role at [Company Name].\\n\\nHere are the proposed details again:\\n  • Date: [Date]\\n  • Time: [Time]\\n  • Platform: [Platform]\\n  • Duration: [Duration]\\n\\nPlease let us know if you’re available or suggest alternative times that work for you.\\n\\nThank you, and I look forward to your reply.\\n\\nBest regards,\\n[Your Name]\\n[Your Title]\\n[Company Name]\\n[Contact Information]\\n```\"}"}
